description: Dale’s Fried Pies started when Dale Mackey began making fried pies for her friends and family in Knoxville, Tennessee. Encouraged by their positive responses, she decided to build a mobile pie stand to bring to farmer’s markets, festivals and private events. Dale’s Fried Pies officially opened in August of 2012 and is now available for your next event.You can't go wrong with a homemade fried pie!
name: Dale's Fried Pies
